but not everyone goes back with hope in their hearts.

11
00:02:11,714 --> 00:02:16,302
This place is still the border.

12
00:02:16,302 --> 00:02:21,306
The border between exploding hope and severe devastation.

13
00:02:25,019 --> 00:02:33,919
Between life and death, where a beginning and the smell of blood coexist.

14
00:02:41,778 --> 00:02:50,140
